name: CLI.AI
description: CLI.AI is decentralized private cloud infrastructure provider, AI development terminal, and market place for open-source AI apps on Solana. We seek to be the premier permissionless private cloud provider for AI computation in the Web3 space. Additionally, we've designed custom hardware accelerators for a variety of applications ranging from LLM inference to edge-vision processing. CLI.AI is a rare breed in the Crypto space as we are a vertically integrated organization.
